Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1128
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 22-9.5.
Synopsis: Prohibited discrimination in housing. Expands the Indiana
fair housing statute to prohibit discrimination on the basis of a person's:
(1) source of income; (2) military active duty status; or (3) veteran
status. Defines "source of income", "active duty", and "veteran" for
purposes of the statute.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Pack
January 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Financial Institutions.
